    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>To get up and rendering with Stylized Looks in Blender is very straightforward and only requires a few simple steps.<br/><br/></p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksHeader.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708681&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksHeader.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708681&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638774\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksHeader.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638744\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0b6a8d40-f36c-4b7e-aa5d-7b5bd0181085\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"0086ab91-1930-44d2-b395-1bae8885f6e7\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><p class=\"title\">RenderMan Materials</p><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Make sure you add a light to your scene and attach a RenderMan material to your objects before rendering with Stylized Looks.</p></div></div><p><br/></p><ol><li><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\">Right-click in the viewport and select </span><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\">RenderMan </strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\">→ </span><strong>Stylized</strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\"><strong> Looks</strong> →</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\"> Stylized Looks Editor</strong><br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksOne.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708479&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksOne.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708479&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638771\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksOne.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638744\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ca87e081-b59a-4f94-8f60-0d7522f84158\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><hr/></li><li> Enable Stylized Looks, select an object, and then select a PxrStylizedControl from Attach Stylized Pattern.  <br/><br/>Pressing OK will now create and attach the required PxrStylizedControl nodes to the PxrSurface of the robot model.  <br/>The PxrStylizedControl network is required to be attached to every object in your scene and allows for individual shading control of each object.<br/><br/>This can also be achieved by selecting an object and <strong>RenderMan </strong>→ <strong>Stylized Looks</strong> → <strong>Attach Stylized Pattern</strong> → <strong>PxrStylizedControl<br/></strong><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksTwo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708479&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksTwo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708479&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638768\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksTwo.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638744\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6be0462b-314f-469f-a606-6d26520d1dc7\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/><br/><hr/></li><li>Using the RenderMan Stylized Editor, you can now begin to add in Stylized Filters to begin creating your unique Stylized Look.<br/><br/>In this example, we'll add in a PxrStylizedHatching Filter<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksFour.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708239&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksFour.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708239&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638762\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksFour.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638744\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"25c67f03-a459-4ee2-b045-97a5cb22b49e\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><hr/></li><li>Now, fire up the IPR, and your scene will now be rendering in Stylized Looks <br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksFive.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708238&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksFive.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708238&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638759\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksFive.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638744\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f59902b6-96c7-4b2b-9d7a-59afdee0b823\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/>Note:  In this example, the default settings have been tweaked in the following :<br/><br/>a) Signal Energy From : <strong>Albedo AOV</strong><br/>b) Blending Mode : <strong>Weighted</strong><br/>c) Blend Black Darkest : <strong>ON</strong><br/>d) Projection : <strong>Screen</strong><br/>e) Hatching Frequency : <strong>4<br/><br/></strong>You are now up and rendering with Stylized Looks! <br/>Your creative adventure into NPR has started and don't forget that the power of Stylized Looks comes when you begin to combine a variety of Stylized Filters together to create your own unique styles and looks.<br/><br/>Stylized Looks also ships with several fun presets to get you started.  You can find these inside the RenderMan Preset Browser<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksPresets.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708238&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638744/RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksPresets.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432708238&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638756\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_StylizedLooksPresets.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638744\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f5934ff5-ad1d-4e55-adc9-7afa6299d0bf\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/></li></ol><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>"
    }
  },
